    "speaker": "",
    "content": "挑战"
  },
  {
    "id": 14101,
    "stepId": 1,
    "type": "talk",
    "param": "513101#610011608",
    "option_param": "",
    "single": 0,
    "speaker": "亚齐",
    "content": "黑暗不值得畏惧，那其中并没有危险。"
  },
  {
    "id": 14101,
    "stepId": 2,
    "type": "talk",
    "param": "513101#0",
    "option_param": "",
    "single": 0,
    "speaker": "亚齐",
    "content": "那些本不存在的怪物只存在于分不清想象和现实的孩子心里……"
  },
  {
    "id": 14101,
    "stepId": 3,
    "type": "talk",
    "param": "513101#610011609",
    "option_param": "",
    "single": 0,
    "speaker": "亚齐",
    "content": "我不是这样的孩子……对吗？"
  },
  {
    "id": 14102,
    "stepId": 5,
    "type": "talk",
    "param": "513101#0",
    "option_param": "",
    "single": 0,
    "speaker": "亚齐",
    "content": "呼……"
  },
  {
    "id": 14102,
    "stepId": 6,
    "type": "talk",
    "param": "513101#0",
    "option_param": "",
    "single": 0,
    "speaker": "亚齐",
    "content": "还好，它们并不危险。我该回家去了……"
  },
  {
    "id": 14211,
    "stepId": 1,
    "type": "tips",
    "param": "",
    "option_param": "",
    "single": 0,
    "speaker": "",
